description: I love it when a true bondage lover like Wenona keeps coming back to WB. We get to know each other well enough that stepping up the play comes naturally to us. I've known for a while now that she is VERY ticklish. I took good advantage of that fact in scene two. To be fair, I gave her a choice between full wrists-only suspension while being flogged or being tickled. And, we FINALLY got to do something we both have been dying to try again- inverted suspension in the Houdini tank! This is one HOT update!
title: Wenona
